profile.bio:
French Free software enthusiast, I’m using Arch Linux, KDE, Firefox, Thunderbird, Pidgin.
I use Bépo and a TypeMatrix keyboard everyday.
I love Python and Rust.
I speak French, English, and I learn German, Japanese and Esperanto
